[Main]
Name=Gray3POnThrow
Type=Function
Subtype=tigcc.a
Header Files=gray3p.h
Definition=void Gray3POnThrow (void);
See Also=gray3p.h/Gray3POn, gray3p.h/Gray3POff, error.h/

[Library Call]
Asm=1

[Description]
Activates grayscale mode, throwing an error if unsuccessful.

[Explanation]
Gray3POnThrow works like <A HREF="$$LINK(gray3p.h/Gray3POn)">Gray3POn</A>, except that it
throws an error if it could not turn on grayscale successfully.

